</div>

  </div>

      </div>

      

      


      
          <p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="1">Eric Ollerenshaw Retweeted Abbi Boyle</p>

    Replying to <span class="username u-dir u-textTruncate" dir="ltr">@<b>VoteOllerenshaw</b></span>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">I'm proud to have been involved in setting this scheme up. I'd encourage anyone with an interest in politics to apply.<a href="https://t.co/UaCeBENwxq" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/ukparliament/status/865139910155550720" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/ukparliament/status/865139910155550720"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/ukparliament/s</span><span class="invisible">tatus/865139910155550720</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>

      <li class="embed-link js-actionEmbedTweet" data-nav="embed_tweet">
        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Embed Tweet</button>
      </li>
  </ul>
</div>

</div>

  </div>

      </div>

      

      


      
          <p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="1">Mark Prisk MP Retweeted Eric Ollerenshaw</p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Your choice at <a href="/hashtag/GE2017?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>GE2017</b></a>: a coalition of <a href="/hashtag/chaos?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>chaos</b></a> creating uncertainty and risk - or strong, stable leadership with Theresa May<a href="https://t.co/6WMijSqiMn" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/6WMijSqiMn</a></p>

  if(window.ttft){
    window.ttft.recordMilestone('page', document.getElementById('swift-page-name').getAttribute('content'));
    window.ttft.recordMilestone('section', document.getElementById('swift-section-name').getAttribute('content'));
    window.ttft.recordMilestone('client_record_time', window.ttft.now());
  }
